style.art_style: Chibi, Super Deformed (SD), Cartoon, 2D Illustration, Minimalist Cartoon
style.technique: Flat colors, Thick, solid dark brown or black outlines (consistent thickness), Minimal to no shading (flat shading only), Highly simplified forms
style.color_palette: Limited, Muted, Pastel-like skin tones (light peach), Earthy hair colors (dark brown), Primary uniform colors (white, black), Consistent prominent rosy cheeks (circular blush)
style.lighting: Flat lighting, Even illumination, No strong shadows or highlights, Ambient light

character.hair: Short, Dark brown, Rounded bangs, Two low pigtails, Smooth flat texture
character.eyes: Small, simple black dot eyes or thin lines for closed/squinted expressions. No visible pupils, irises, or whites of the eyes. A single, short, curved line often represents an eyelash, typically positioned centrally above the eye.
character.face: Round face, Prominent rosy cheeks (circular blush), Small dot or tiny inverted 'v' nose, Simple line mouth (curved line, open oval, or straight line) for various expressions, Minimal features, Consistent short distance between nose and mouth.
character.outfit: White short-sleeved collared shirt with two visible buttons, Black pleated skirt, Uniform style
character.accessories: None (uniform elements are part of the main outfit)
character.body_proportions: Extreme Chibi or Super Deformed (SD) style, consistently 1.8 to 2-head proportion, where the head constitutes roughly 45-55% of the total body height, resulting in a very compact, top-heavy, and squat build.
character.limb_proportions: Arms and legs are consistently very short and thick, contributing significantly to the squat, compact, and top-heavy appearance. Arms typically end around the waist level when extended, and legs consistently make up less than 30% of the total body height. Limb length is strictly maintained across all poses and expressions.
character.torso_shape: Short and wide, almost rectangular or slightly barrel-shaped, with minimal waist definition. Appears compact and solid.
character.hand_style: Highly simplified, mitten-style with a distinct, small, rounded protrusion for the thumb, while the remaining fingers are merged into a single rounded, blob-like mass. No individual fingers (other than the thumb) are depicted.

composition.pose: Simple, expressive poses such as standing, jumping, pouting, arms crossed, huddled (e.g., crying), or crying. Poses are generally frontal, slight 3/4 view, or occasionally a direct back view.
composition.angle: Eye-level or slightly low-angle, Straight-on or slight 3/4 view
composition.background: Plain background, Solid color background (transparent or white), Minimalist
composition.depth_of_field: Flat depth of field, Everything in sharp focus, No bokeh effect
